title: The.Wackness.Jonathan.Levine.Script.Screenplay
description:
This film opened today(July 4) in limited release around the States.  Enjoy.

It&#039;s the summer of 1994, and the streets of New York are pulsing with hip-hop. Set against this backdrop, Luke Shapiro (Josh Peck) spends his last summer before college selling dope throughout New York City, trading it with his shrink (Ben Kingsley) for therapy, while crushing on his step-daughter (Olivia Thirlby).
